<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>ạ̉skb rwḥk ʿlynạ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- ạ̉skb rwḥk ʿlynạ .. ymlạnạ wygẖṭynạ
 tbqạlk ṭwl lyạlynạ .. tsbyḥ
 1- ạ̹nt ạlly tḥwl nwḥ lrqṣ .. jrḥ lfrḥ wạ̉gẖạny ktyr
 wtḥwl rmạd ljmạl .. wbdl ạlyạ̉s rdạʾ tsbyḥ
 2- ạ̹nt ạlly tqwl kn fykwn .. kl ạlkwn ykẖḍʿ lạ̹ydyk
 wạnt ạlly bklmẗ thdy bḥwr .. wkl ạlryḥ bysmʿ lyk
 3- ạ̹nt ạlly tkwn lsẖʿbk nwr .. wsṭ ạllyl tkwn lyhm nhạr
 bsḥạbẗ wʿạmwd mn nạr .. tqwdhm dạymaⁿạ wsṭ ạlạ̉kẖṭạr</lyrics>
